        WHERE ([r].[Name] IN (N'VanThu') AND ([f].[Id] = @__functionId_1)) AND ([p].[CanRead] = 1))
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END" (0723d8ff)
